Distribution. Present material from Australia : Port Lincoln, South Australia ; Port Jackson, Cape Jervis, Broken Bay, Pyrmount and Caloundra, New South Wales ; Wilson’s Promontory, Victoria; Tasman Sea and St. Helens, Tasmania. Previous reports include New Zealand (
Fabricius 1775
;
1793
).

